  "title": "💼 Marketing Associate Wanted! Learn • Earn • Grow 🌱",
  "description": "<p>🚀 <strong>About Us</strong><br>\nWe’re a fast-growing outsourced sales &amp; marketing company working with major brands across telco, NGOs, and more. We’re looking for confident, motivated individuals to join our face-to-face marketing team!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>💪 <strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Represent clients at events &amp; roadshows</li>\n  <li>Build brand awareness and close sales</li>\n  <li>Work in a fun, team-driven environment</li>\n  <li>Learn leadership &amp; business skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p>🎯 <strong>What You’ll Get</strong><br>\n✅ Full training (no experience needed)<br>\n✅ Uncapped earnings &amp; bonuses<br>\n✅ 1-to-1 mentorship<br>\n✅ Career progression to leadership<br>\n✅ Travel opportunities</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>👀 <strong>We’re Looking For</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>People who are outgoing, driven &amp; love a challenge</li>\n  <li>Team players with a positive attitude</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Ready to grow, earn, and have fun while doing it?</strong><br>\n👉 Apply now — immediate start available!</p>",
